trans-unit.source: Represents a data point that is stored in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPointCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et datapunkt som er lagret i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPointCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The DataPoint class stores properties associated with data as well as data point values.
trans-unit.target: DataPoint butikker klasseegenskaper tilknyttet som data verdiene for datapunktene.

trans-unit.source: For example, a data point has a value, but it also has a color property, background image property, background gradient property, and so forth.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel et datapunkt har en verdi, men den har også en color-egenskap bakgrunnen Bildeegenskapen, bakgrunnen gradering egenskapen og så videre.

trans-unit.source: For more information about data point properties, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPointCustomProperties> class overview topic.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om dataene egenskaper, kan du se den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPointCustomProperties>klassen oversikt Oversiktsemnet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPointCustomProperties>

trans-unit.source: Each data point consists of an X-value and one or more Y-values.
trans-unit.target: Hvert datapunkt består av en X-verdien og én eller flere Y-verdier.

trans-unit.source: The X-value can be zero, or you can set this explicitly.
trans-unit.target: X-verdien kan være null, eller du kan angi dette eksplisitt.

trans-unit.source: Only one Y-value per point is required for all chart types except bubble, candlestick and stock charts.
trans-unit.target: Bare én Y-verdien per punkt kreves for alle diagramtyper unntatt boble, candlestick og lager.

trans-unit.source: These chart types require more than one Y-value because one data point consists of multiple values.
trans-unit.target: Disse diagramtypene krever mer enn én Y-verdien fordi ett datapunkt består av flere verdier.

trans-unit.source: For example, to plot one stock chart column, four values are required: high, low, open and close values.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel for å tegne én stock diagramkolonne fire verdier kreves: høy lav, og åpne Lukk verdier.

trans-unit.source: Data can be added at either design time or run time; you can also use data-binding at run time.
trans-unit.target: Data som kan legges til i enten utformingen eller kjøretid; Du kan også bruke databinding på kjøretidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that indicates whether a data point is marked as empty.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som indikerer om et datapunkt er merket som tomt.

trans-unit.source: Set this property to `true` to mark a data point as an empty point.
trans-unit.target: Sett denne egenskapen til `true` å merke et datapunkt som et tomt punkt.

trans-unit.source: Alternatively one of the `InsertEmptyPoints` methods in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataManipulator> class can be used to mark missing data as empty points.
trans-unit.target: Alternativt én av de `InsertEmptyPoints` metodene i den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataManipulator>klassen kan brukes til å merke manglende data som tomt punkt.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataManipulator>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.EmptyPointStyle%2A> property determines how empty points are displayed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.EmptyPointStyle%2A>egenskapen bestemmer hvordan tomt punkt vises.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.EmptyPointStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the point is marked as an empty point; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis punktet er merket som et tomt punkt; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Sets the X-value and one or more Y-values of the data point.

trans-unit.source: Use the SetValueXY method to set the value(s) of a data point at run-time.
trans-unit.target: Bruk metoden SetValueXY for å angi verdiene for et datapunkt ved kjøretid.

trans-unit.source: Note that if you set the X-value to a value other than zero (0), a scatter plot will be generated.
trans-unit.target: Merk at hvis du angir X-verdien til en annen verdi enn null (0), genereres XY tegning.

trans-unit.source: Only one Y-value per point is required for all chart types except for bubble, candlestick and stock charts.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValuesPerPoint%2A> property determines the maximum number of Y-values that all data points in a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> can have.

trans-unit.source: If you specify more than the allowable number of Y-values, an exception will be raised.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir mer enn det maksimale antallet Y-verdier, vil du starter et unntak.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the X-value of a data point.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir X-verdien for et datapunkt.

trans-unit.source: All chart types can be displayed as either scatter plots or as non-scatter plots, because both X-values and Y-values can be set.
trans-unit.target: Alle diagramtyper kan vise som enten XY inntegninger eller ikke XY inntegninger fordi både X- og Y-verdier kan angis.

trans-unit.source: Setting an X-value will result in a scatter plot, whereas not setting this property—which is equivalent to setting it to zero—will result in a non-scatter plot.
trans-unit.target: Angi en X-verdien, fører det XY tegning, mens angir ikke denne egenskapen, som tilsvarer det å sette verdien til null, resulterer i tegning ikke XY.

trans-unit.source: For example, to draw a point chart type, add data points that have X-values of zero.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel for å tegne et diagram punkttype legge datapunkter som har X-verdier på null.

trans-unit.source: To display a traditional scatter chart, add data points that have X-values other than zero.
trans-unit.target: For å vise et tradisjonell punktdiagram, legger du til datapunkter som har X-verdier enn null.

trans-unit.source: The X-values of data points are not required to be set.
trans-unit.target: X-verdiene for datapunktene er må angis.

trans-unit.source: If they are not set, data points are plotted sequentially, using their index values from the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPointCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis de ikke er angitt, tegnes datapunkt sekvensielt, ved hjelp av indeksverdiene fra <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPointCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPointCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> that represents the X-value of a data point.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> som representerer X-verdien for et datapunkt.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Y-value(s) of a data point.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir Y-verdiene for et datapunkt.

trans-unit.source: The YValues property is used to set the Y-values of data points.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen YValues brukes til å angi Y-verdier for datapunkt.

trans-unit.source: Only one Y-value per point is required for all chart types except bubble, candlestick and stock charts.
trans-unit.target: Bare én Y-verdien per punkt kreves for alle diagramtyper unntatt boble, candlestick og lager.

trans-unit.source: These chart types require more than one Y-value because one data point consists of multiple values.
trans-unit.target: Disse diagramtypene krever mer enn én Y-verdien fordi ett datapunkt består av flere verdier.

trans-unit.source: For example, to plot one stock chart column, four values are required: high, low, open and close values.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel for å tegne én stock diagramkolonne fire verdier kreves: høy lav, og åpne Lukk verdier.

trans-unit.source: The YValues property returns an array of `double` values when used to retrieve the Y-values.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen YValues returnerer en matrise av `double` verdier når brukes til å hente Y-verdier.

trans-unit.source: **Important** The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValuesPerPoint%2A> property determines the maximum number of Y-values that all data points in a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> can have.
trans-unit.target: **Viktig** den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValuesPerPoint%2A>egenskapen angir maksimalt antall Y-verdier som alle datapunktene i en <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>kan ha.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValuesPerPoint%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you specify more than the allowable number of Y-values, an exception will be raised.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir mer enn det maksimale antallet Y-verdier, vil du starter et unntak.
